#   FCC Al  
#   Check the validity of the dE/d(tsmear)=-kT*entropy relationship
#   It does not work for occopt=6, likely due to the
#   problem advertised in the help file, namely the occurence of negative
#   occupation numbers.

 ndtset 12  udtset 4 3

 ngkpt 4 4 4   nkpt 10

 occopt1? 4
 occopt2? 5
 occopt3? 6
 occopt4? 7

 tsmear?1 0.01d0 
 tsmear?2 0.0099d0 
 tsmear?3 0.0101d0 

